     </svg><span class="text-lg font-medium">TikTok</span> </a> <a id="link-youtube" href="https://youtube.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="glass-btn flex items-center gap-4 px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl w-full animate-in" style="animation-delay:0.7s">
